\c 92
\s Rwiyo rwokurumbidza Jehovha
\d Pisarema, rwiyo rweSabata.
\p
\v 1 Zvakanaka kuvonga Jehovha, Nokuimbira zita renyu nziyo dzokurumbidza, imi Wokumusorosoro;
\v 2 Kuparidza unyoro hwenyu mangwanani,
\s Nokutendeka kwenyu usiku hwose,
\p
\v 3 Nechinoridzwa chine ungiso gumi, nomutengeranwa;
\s Nezwi rakanaka pambira.
\p
\v 4 Nokuti imi, Jehovha, makandifadza nezvamakaita;
\s Ndichafara kwazvo namabasa amaoko enyu.
\p
\v 5 Mabasa enyu akakura seiko, Jehovha!
\s Mifungo yenyu yakadzika kwazvo.
\p
\v 6 Asina njere haazvizivi;
\s Benzi harinzwisisi izvozvi,
\p
\v 7 Kana vakaipa vachimera souswa, Uye kana vaiti vose vezvakaipa vachikura;
\s Zvinoitwa kuti vaparadzwe nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 8 kSi imi SehoNha, rtâ€˜-ux kuIrmsotc) nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 9 Nokuti tarirai, Jehovha, vavengi venyu,
\s Nokuti tarirai, Jehovha, vavengi venyu vachaparara;
\s Vaiti vose vezvakaipa
\s vachaparadzirwa.
\s lo Asi runyanga rwangu makarusimudza sorunyanga rwenyati;
\s Ndakazodzwa namafuta matsva.
\p
\v 11 Ziso rangu rakaona zvakaitirwa vavengi vangu,
\s Nzeve dzangu dzakanzwa zvakaitirwa
\s vaiti vezvakaipa, vakandimukira.
\p
\v 12 Akarurama achamera somuchindwe; Achakura somusidhari paRebhanoni.
\p
\v 13 Vakasimwa mumba maJehovha Vachakura muvazhe dzaMwari wedu.
\p
\v 14 Vacharamba vachibereka zvibereko pakukwegura kwavo;
\p Vachava vanyoro navatsva;
\v 15 Kuti vaparidze kuti Jehovha akarurama;
\s Ndiye dombo rangu,
\s hapana chinhu chisina kururama maari.
